<item>
            <title>[RAVE-298] Page manipulations are unchecked</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/RAVE-298</link>
                <project id="12311290" key="RAVE">Rave</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently it&apos;s possible to add/move/delete a widget on a page that does not belong to the logged in user by changing request parameters or the id in the url. Checks must be added to page and widget manipulations if the user that does the manipulations are performed by the owner.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12526494">RAVE-298</key>
            <summary>Page manipulations are unchecked</summary>
